Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.04,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\be1\bord1\fs70}尼鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.04,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\blur2\shad3\fs70}尼鲁
